{"word":"G3643 - ὀλιγωρέω - oligōréō - ol-ig-o-reh'-o - Despise","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀλιγωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oligōréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ol-ig-o-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Despise</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அற்பமாக எண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to care little for, to regard lightly, to make small account of"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3641 - ὀλίγος - olígos - ol-ee'-gos/3641\">G3641</a> and <b>&#x03C9;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;</b> <b>o&#x0304;ra</b> (&ldquo;care&rdquo;); to <i>have little regard</i> for, that is, to <i>disesteem:</i> - despise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3640/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G3641/3641\">G3641</a>, <a href=\"#/G3642/3642\">G3642</a>, <a href=\"#/G3643/3643\">G3643</a>"}]}